<!DOCTYPE html>

<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head runat="server">
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
    <title></title>
    <style>
        #BlockLeft {
            float: left;
            padding-top: 235px;
            width: 285px;
        }
        #BlockRight {
            float: left;
            padding-top: 220px;
